The '''media repository''' is a directory in SVN where we store the blender files, the original textures/images in gimp/inkscape format, etc.

You may obtain the media repository by obtaining URL
<code>https://supertuxkart.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/supertuxkart/media/trunk</code>

Under Unix, the checkout command-line would look like :
<code>svn checkout https://supertuxkart.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/supertuxkart/media/trunk stk_media_repo</code>

You can also browse it online [http://supertuxkart.svn.sourceforge.net/viewvc/supertuxkart/media/trunk/ at sourceforge using ViewVC].
